text: I started to knock together something very basic with Dash... It can monitor orders by customer strategy ref at the moment. It won't be too hard to add a "delete all orders"button. When it is tidier I can share it if people are interested. Due to Dash limitations I think it can only be very basic, but it should handle my use case.
